{"tid":2025220,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊延攬「小島製作前創始成員今泉健一郎」與 「Ubisoft 遊戲總監」加入 積極擴展中國以外市場","createTime":"2020-05-20T06:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:57:09.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"723ad08dab00d3172d83f7ef3f7d697953599a33","tid":2025220,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"　　中國遊戲大廠騰訊積極擴展遊戲研發版圖，確定延攬小島製作（Kojima Productions）創始成員今泉健一郎與《最後一戰 4》設計總監 Scott Warner 等遊戲業界資深人才加入騰訊。<br />\n <br />\nimage<br />\n <br />\n　　今泉健一郎為小島製作的共同創辦人，在 KONAMI 時期就參與《潛龍諜影》系列多部作品的開發，是小島秀夫多年的合作夥伴，而今泉健一郎將出任騰訊遊戲歐洲總部的製作總監。<br />\n <br />\n　　Scott Warner 曾經在 343 Industries、美商藝電、Oculus VR、Ubisoft 等遊戲廠商任職，並曾負責像是《最後一戰 4》、《戰地風雲：強硬路線》等遊戲開發工作。如今 Scott Warner 在離開 Ubisoft 美國團隊遊戲總監職位後，將領導騰訊遊戲旗下天美工作室位於美國加州的大型遊戲團隊，而該團隊最近正在募集人才將開發與《寶可夢》相關的授權遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n　　Scott Warner 也在個人 Twitter 上宣布，他將擔任研發團隊的總監、負責 AAA 級專案，並且透露團隊正在擴大招募人才。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOWMCBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOWMCBB.jpg&h=6680bd6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　騰訊曾經透露，他們希望聘請經驗豐富的資深遊戲開發人才，來打造世界一流的團隊，建立國際基地、來為中國以外的玩家製作任何平台的新遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n　　遊戲業界則認為，騰訊此舉主要是因應中國遊戲市場成長速度不若以往爆發，加上中國政府對遊戲採取審批制度、造成每年遊戲上市款數受到限制，使得騰訊改尋求在海外擴大玩家族群與收入。"},{"pid":"7886659cd1ed633327a1ac247956b1209652c6b3","tid":2025220,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"究竟收咗幾多人工先肯join啲垃圾支那工作室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816774791cafc961639afdee2a1da743230120f8","tid":2025220,"uid":199120,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔比自己嘅機民打機<br />\n但要賺人地國人嘅機民錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利害了我的国<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbf7fc9c6e066525e1e7fa68ca9bcf32bab270c","tid":2025220,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"騰訊出3A驚 人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"0826cd90e1411b4d9c1f43009152189a3c97fd0c","tid":2025220,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n陣間改錯名又比你bam"},{"pid":"289b622aff3ae13bd83a986fabeadc9a2d2c47ce","tid":2025220,"uid":76216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"小島工作室出名係因為小島而唔係其他人<br />\n<br />\n係一個明星效應<br />\n<br />\n其他人係明星效應之下=垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3d3552a637c9fda6e3366175e906b61a5f7895","tid":2025220,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"289b622aff3ae13bd83a986fabeadc9a2d2c47ce","tid":2025220,"uid":76216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"小島工作室出名係因為小島而唔係其他人<br />\n<br />\n係一個明星效應<br />\n<br />\n其他人係明星效應之下=垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ec68aec1e71d6f32af149c208a0072d8f91d45","tid":2025220,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da3d3552a637c9fda6e3366175e906b61a5f7895","tid":2025220,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"289b622aff3ae13bd83a986fabeadc9a2d2c47ce","tid":2025220,"uid":76216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"小島工作室出名係因為小島而唔係其他人<br />\n<br />\n係一個明星效應<br />\n<br />\n其他人係明星效應之下=垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:46:37.000Z